interactables.name: Interactable Kitchen
dialogue: There's nothing but a breadbox here.

interactables.name: Interactable Cabinet 1
dialogue: It's full of spices of all kinds.

interactables.name: Interactable Book
dialogue: This book is exactly like the one from your dreams. The pages are full of runes.

interactables.name: Interactable Cabinet 2
dialogue: These clothes belong to your mom.

interactables.name: Interactable Cabinet 4
dialogue: These clothes belong to your dad. Some of your old clothes are here, too.

interactables.name: Interactable Bed 1
dialogue: You consider taking a nap, but you avoid the temptation.

interactables.name: Interactable Kitchenette
dialogue: Your mom makes delicious meals here.
